::Orchestra::

    Orchestra changed his comm-link over to Blacknightmare.

    "Sure thing, love," Orchestra said, reminding her of their relationship
also.

    Then, he switched back over to Darkfate.

    "Nevermind, master!" he said.

    Then with that, Orchestra headed off to Blacknightmare's coordinates.
